62216.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62216.description: A concert promoter wants to send SpongeBob and Squidward on the road, until greedy Mr. Krabs decides to manage them—and their “world tour”—himself.

62217.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
62217.description: When the group arrives at a small Earth Kingdom mining town, they see an earthbender, named Haru, who is practicing his ability, but he runs away when Katara tries to confront him about it. They soon learn that the Fire Nation has taken over the town, that earthbending is forbidden and all earthbenders are taken away to an offshore prison. However, when an elderly man is trapped in a collapsed mine, Katara urges Haru to use his powers to save the man's life, but then, the old man reports Haru to the authorities. Katara blames herself for his predicament and she vows to rescue him, but will she succeed?

62218.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
62218.description: When Aang is assigned to help defend a town from a monster that has been plaguing the town, his lack of ability and knowledge becomes obvious, as he doesn't know what to do. However, when Sokka tries to rush to Aang's rescue during the fight, he himself becomes captured and is taken away by the monster, which turns out to be from the spirit world. Aang promises Katara that he'll find Sokka and bring him back, but with Aang even doubting himself, will he be capable of finding where the monster went?

62219.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62219.description: Plankton hasn't tried to steal the secret formula in a while...and that's making Mr. Krabs nervous! // When Patrick discovers the pineapple's library, SpongeBob introduces him to the wonderful world of book learning!

62220.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62220.description: Plankton goes to jail, but the secret formula is taken as evidence! SpongeBob and Mr. Krabs plot to get it back. // Sandy struggles to build a ship-in-a-bottle before a big contest, so SpongeBob calls in a little extra help.

62221.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
62221.description: Tiger Claw returns and intends to destroy the Turtles at any cost.

62222.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
62222.description: Mikey discovers that a new mutant is trying to attack and capture people using living pizzas, but he struggles to convince the others who don't believe him.

62223.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
62223.description: When Temutai kidnaps a kung fu master, Shifu turns to Po for help.

62224.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
62224.description: Po discovers his dad, Mr. Ping, is dating Scorpion, but he has trouble trusting his former enemy who claims to no longer be evil.

62225.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
62225.description: Lemmy the robot returns from Mars. Unknowingly a space squid has stowed away in his chest cavity. // Careless Alice over chlorinates the otter habitat and Marlene’s fur is bleached. Her new look captivates the attention of the other zoo animals.

62226.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
62226.description: The zoo animals are suffering a heat wave. The penguins have a plan to beat the heat, but they need Alice out of the way. With her gone, they get to work. // Private is smitten with the zoo nurse. The only way he can see her is if he gets injured.

62227.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62227.description: Plankton hasn't tried to steal the secret formula in a while...and that's making Mr. Krabs nervous! // When Patrick discovers the pineapple's library, SpongeBob introduces him to the wonderful world of book learning!

62228.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62228.description: Plankton goes to jail, but the secret formula is taken as evidence! SpongeBob and Mr. Krabs plot to get it back. // Sandy struggles to build a ship-in-a-bottle before a big contest, so SpongeBob calls in a little extra help.

62229.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62229.description: The long-lost episode of Mermaid Man is finally showing on TV, but will SpongeBob make it home in time to watch? // Karen gets a computer virus, and it's up to SpongeBob to get it out of her!

62230.title: Nella The Princess Knight
62230.description: Nella and her friends take part in an action packed Go-kart race! // Nella and Blaine search for the mysterious Moat Lake Monster.

62231.title: Nella The Princess Knight
62231.description: After a display of true courage, Trinket receives a sparkling new carriage from the Unicorn of the Lake. // Nella and Cici combine their talents to form The Castlehaven Rescue Club.

62232.title: Bubble Guppies
62232.description: A friendly squirrel gives Nonny an acorn that will someday grow into a tree! Join the Bubble Guppies in learning all about trees -the animals that live in them, the fruit that grows on them, and how they can help them.

62233.title: Bubble Guppies
62233.description: Ahoy, mateys! The Bubble Guppies are going on a pirate adventure! Gil and Molly meet a friendly pirate with a problem - he can't find his pirate treasure! So with a treasure map in hand Gil and Molly and all their Guppy friends set sail to find where X marks the spot!

62234.title: Dora the Explorer
62234.description: It's Mother's Day, and Dora wants to help Papi bake Mamá a special cake. But three key ingredients are missing: bananas, nuts and chocolate.

62235.title: Dora the Explorer
62235.description: Go-go-go-golden Explorers! Dora and her friends have formed a soccer team and are playing the big Dinosaurs. Can Dora kick the ball into the net and score a goal?

62236.title: Rusty Rivets
62236.description: When a rare bird builds his nest in a dangerous location and can't be persuaded to move, Rusty and the gang rebuild his habitat. // Rusty and Ruby build a cupcake flinging machine that goes out of control.

62237.title: Rusty Rivets
62237.description: When the Bits find a satellite crashed in the scrapyard, Rusty has to find a way to get the satellite bit back home to space! // Rusty and the gang must move a sick fish to the Nature Park for treatment.

62238.title: Blaze And The Monster Machines
62238.description: When Blaze and Starla encounter a herd of cows wandering out in the desert, they must embark on a wild west adventure to bring them back to Starla’s barn.

62239.title: Blaze And The Monster Machines
62239.description: It's the day of the Dragon Island Duel, a race around tropical Dragon Island! But when Crusher cheats and sends Blaze away before the race, AJ must set out to rescue his best friend and bring him back to the starting line.

62240.title: PAW Patrol
62240.description: Impressed by the Paw Patrol's rescues, Alex sets up his own mini-Patrol, recruitng Chickaletta, Cali, Turtle, and Bunny. // Alex loses his first tooth, then really loses it.The tooth must be located before the Tooth Fairy comes!

62241.title: PAW Patrol
62241.description: While camping, Marshall and the PAW Patrol help Alex learn about Fire Safety! // It seems like a regular day in Adventure Bay as the Paw Patrol is called to duty. But the pups are in for a surprise - PAW Patrol Appreciation Day!

62242.title: PAW Patrol
62242.description: The pups are learning the ancient art of Pup-Fu! They'll need it to get back Sensei Farmer Yumi's ancient martial arts scroll, after Mayor Humdinger's Kit-tastrophe Crew use their Cat-Jitsu skills to steal it!

62243.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62243.description: An imprisoned Plankton teams up with his fellow inmates to break out of jail and steal the Krabby Patty secret formula. // SpongeBob replaces his broken spatula with one from Plankton, which may or may not have magical powers.

62244.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62244.description: When a volcanic vent under Goo Lagoon becomes active, a giant volatile gas bubble rises to the surface. Plankton manages to get his evil little hands on the bubble and threatens to pop it, covering all of Bikini Bottom in goo, unless Mr. Krabs gives him the Krabby Patty formula. It's up to SpongeBob, Patrick and Sandy to find a way to thwart Plankton and save the town

62245.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62245.description: Mr. Krabs gets trapped in Bikini Bottom’s brand-new bank, and it’s up to SpongeBob & Patrick to save him. // After failing again to steal the Krabby Patty formula, Plankton gets a pet to cheer himself up.

62246.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
62246.description: King Julien is literally bounced out of his kingdom and onto the New York streets. A kindly old lady thinks he's a cat and swoops him up. He's encroaching on another's turf, though - the apartment's already home to a feline-impersonator, a female ferret named Zoe. Julien is taken with Zoe, and puts on his best seduction moves. Will the street-smart ferret succumb to his kingly charms? Smart money says... you never know! Action Reaction: Skipper is forced to live his worst nightmare when he's doused with Inflatium and stress causes him to blow up like a balloon. Guess what this means... no more going on missions! Sitting behind a desk doing paperwork instead! Hans takes advantage of the situation and targets a massive weapons lab, and without Skipper the penguins are easily captured. How can Skipper combat the evil puffin if he's in a puffy state?

62247.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
62247.description: Kowalski has a rival, if you even can call it a rivalry. A Delaware Blue Hen has taken up residence at the zoo, and she has the amazing ability to predict the future! Kowalski doesn't buy the psychic chicken hype and sets out to discredit her. The truth turns out to be far more sinister than a simple sports-pickin' chicken, and Kowalski will have to use all his best moves to wiggle out of this mess. Thumb Drive: The penguins need a thumb, and Maurice's fits the bill nicely. Using the opposable digit thumbprint to break into a secret weapons lab gets the penguins all atwitter. King Julien is unhappy that his right hand man is running around on missions with the birds so he sets out to sabotage the mission. As with most of King Julien's plans, this scheme turns out to be "thumbs down"!

62248.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
62248.description: When Mantis returns to his hometown claiming to be the Dragon Warrior to impress his ex-fiancé, Po pretends to be his sidekick who doesn't know kung fu.

62249.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
62249.description: Shifu tells the citizens of the Valley of Peace that whoever can defeat Po before sunset will become the new Dragon Warrior. When Hundun hears of the challenge, he returns to the village to claim the title.

62250.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
62250.description: Donnie finishes a new batch of retro-mutagen, hoping to save Karai, but the Turtles find themselves hunted by Shredder's new vengeful henchmen. Bebop and Rocksteady!

62251.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
62251.description: Leo doesn't trust Slash when he emerges leading a team called the "Mighty Mutanimals".

62252.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62252.description: In an attempt to get away from SpongeBob, Squidward drives off in his boat as fast as he can, but he is pulled over and ordered to go to boating school. // Mr. Krabs decides to go into the tabloid business.

62253.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62253.description: Pearl's getting ready for her slumber party, but Mr. Krabs' meddling in the party preparations is getting out of control. // SpongeBob decides to enter Gary in a pet show and gives him a makeover after seeing the competition.

62254.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62254.description: SpongeBob and his friends are swept away by a giant wave and find themselves stranded on a remote tropical island. To get back to Bikini Bottom, they need to learn how to surf from enigmatic surf guru, Jack Kahuna Lagun.

62255.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
62255.description: Po realizes he must select a trophy for the Hall of Heroes, but instead finds himself helping a young villager retrieve a rabbit doll that is much more important than it looks.

62256.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
62256.description: Po disguises himself as the merciless villain, Tong Fo, to try and locate a hidden weapon.

62257.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
62257.description: The penguins are inspired after witnessing a good deed executed by a zoo patron. So they set out to perform their own good deeds - penguin's style. When things don't work out as planned, a domino of bad events requires fixing. // While Mort and Private stop to liberate Cheezy Bitz from the zoo vending machine they are both sucked in. Each attempt to escape fails and their only hope is to be rescued, but everyone is searching for them outside of the zoo.

62258.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
62258.description: It's game night and the penguins are playing hot potato with a live bomb. // According to the penguin's intel, the sewer rats are up to something BIG. They need an undercover operative. But who is rat-like enough to pull off such a mission? Mort.

62259.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
62259.description: Leo, worried about Karai, tries to convince the others to rescue her, while a master thief steals Shredder's helmet, and it falls into the Turtles' unsuspecting hands.

62260.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
62260.description: Raph's hot-headed impulsiveness lands him in deep trouble when he accidentally damages a machine that forces him to switch minds with a Kraang.

62261.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62261.description: SpongeBob and Patrick try to join the extreme sports team The Drasticals. // Sandy finds a book of world’s records, and tries to break them all with SpongeBob’s help.

62262.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62262.description: SpongeBob learns his milkshake license has expired, and is forced to go back to the milkshake academy. // Squidward hits his head and reverts to being a baby, and it's up to SpongeBob and Patrick to take care of him.

62263.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62263.description: Squidward finds SpongeBob's diary, and starts reading it out loud in the Krusty Krab. // SpongeBob once again fails his driving test, forcing Mrs. Puff to think outside the box--and off the road.

62264.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
62264.description: When Taotie tries to destroy the Jade Palace and fails, he is sent to prison while his son, Bian Zao, is left behind with Po, who acts like a big brother to the boy who thinks everything is lame!

62265.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
62265.description: While repairs are being made to the noodle shop, Mr. Ping turns the training hall into a restaurant!

62266.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
62266.description: The lemur habitat acquires a new resident, Clemson, and King Julien loves to order him around. Maurice enjoys not having to work, but Mort remains highly suspicious of Clemson, he knows that he is up to something evil. // Kowalski's attempt to super charge his brain backfires and now he's dumber than mud. His lack of intellect starts to comprise the troop's missions. Skipper, Private and Rico must find a cure for him before he hurts someone.

62267.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
62267.description: Private hones in on his cuteness factor and BOOSH! Any witness or potential threat is instantly disabled - adorability has been weaponized. // In the haste of a zoo animal meeting, King Julien and Skipper are agreed to switch places for a single day.

62268.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
62268.description: Aang learns that he must go to the Fire Nation temple during the winter solstice if he wishes to speak with Avatar Roku to see what he must do. However, with Prince Zuko on his trail while he heads straight into the heart of the nation who wants him captured, he realizes that this isn't going to be an easy task. Will Aang be able to talk to Avatar Roku before Zuko finds him?

62269.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
62269.description: After Katara attempts to teach Aang waterbending, she is desperate to improve her abilities. When Katara inadvertently stumbles across a waterbending scroll that can help improve her ability while Aang is looking at a pirate's store, she decides to steal it after she realizes that she couldn't hope to afford it; but will she be capable of stealing from the pirates without causing herself and her friends trouble?

62270.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62270.description: SpongeBob finds a nasty sea urchin living in the Krusty Krab, and tries everything to force it out. // After getting his groceries stolen, Squidward convinces SpongeBob and Sandy to teach him karate.

62271.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62271.description: An imprisoned Plankton teams up with his fellow inmates to break out of jail and steal the Krabby Patty secret formula. // SpongeBob replaces his broken spatula with one from Plankton, which may or may not have magical powers.

62272.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62272.description: When a volcanic vent under Goo Lagoon becomes active, a giant volatile gas bubble rises to the surface. Plankton manages to get his evil little hands on the bubble and threatens to pop it, covering all of Bikini Bottom in goo, unless Mr. Krabs gives him the Krabby Patty formula. It's up to SpongeBob, Patrick and Sandy to find a way to thwart Plankton and save the town

62273.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
62273.description: Leo goes behind Splinter's back when he stages a rescue for Karai, whose desire for revenge against Shredder brings about grave consequences for them all.

62274.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
62274.description: As Donnie becomes increasingly jealous of April and Casey's relationship, April is kidnapped by an evil spirit who intends to drain April's powers.

62275.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
62275.description: When Shifu's con-man father comes back into town, Po finds himself in the middle.

62276.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
62276.description: Po is excited when he discovers a kung fu prodigy, but starts to worry when people seem to prefer the new kid to their beloved Dragon Warrior.

62277.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
62277.description: Private's quirky Uncle Nigel pops in for a quick visit from across the pond. // The boys intercept a fax with cartographic news; Maurice has only 24 hours to live. In order to make Maurice's assumed final day comfortable, the entire zoo bands together.

62278.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
62278.description: Private discovers a stack of lost comic books. Skipper immediately commands their destruction, citing their risky influence. // Shakespeare in the park has inspired Private as he struts around the zoo spouting iambic pentameter laden insults.

62279.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
62279.description: The penguins have had enough of the crazy lemurs 24 hour parting! They hack into the zoo habitat schematic and successfully transfer the lemurs to the petting zoo. // The penguins journey to the bottom of the Atlantic for 100 year-old preserved herring.

62280.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62280.description: Mr. Krabs gets trapped in Bikini Bottom’s brand-new bank, and it’s up to SpongeBob & Patrick to save him. // After failing again to steal the Krabby Patty formula, Plankton gets a pet to cheer himself up.

62281.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62281.description: SpongeBob and Patrick go to see the latest horror film, only to be seemingly stalked by the villain. // SpongeBob holds a séance at the Krusty Krab to learn the recipe for a long-lost sandwich.

62282.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62282.description: SpongeBob will do anything to get to meet his newest hero, Kenny The Cat. // Attempting to get more work out of Squidward, Mr. Krabs spins the story of the monstrous Yeti Crab, which eats lazy workers.
